  ((SELECT id FROM mock_test_bank WHERE exam_type = 'TOPIK_I' AND test_number = 36 ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1), 'listening', 19, '여자 :안녕하세요?수영을 좀 배우려고 하는데요.
